Read `.airlift/HANDOFF.md`.

Before applying the patch, confirm `git rev-parse HEAD` equals {{HEAD}}
(recorded in `.airlift/state.json`). If it differs, do NOT auto-apply -- check
out {{HEAD}} first, or apply with `git apply --3way .airlift/uncommitted.patch`
and resolve conflicts manually.

If HEAD matches AND `.airlift/uncommitted.patch` is non-empty AND your working
tree is clean, apply it with `git apply .airlift/uncommitted.patch`.

Then continue from the Next steps section.
